{"tid":1472333,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"兄弟 出絕招啦 必殺技","createTime":"2019-08-14T14:10:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T15:35:26.000Z","uid":294550,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1ea650ae763c2b738194596a16a2d4fde05a64e2","tid":1472333,"uid":294550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:10:23.000Z","msg":"我地要發起反客為主行動：<br />\n<br />\n轉：我地香港人已經永遠失去左六個手足, 有絲打失明兼毀容, 有幾百個手足面對失去前途, 傳媒越來越紅, 黑社會同軍政府既權力越來越大, 我地既五大訴求連半個都冇被正面回應, 而家我地擔心既卻唔係終有一日全部人一齊入集中營, 而係旅客上唔上到機咁簡單<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">重點：</span><br />\n<br />\n首先我地要表明我地係反共產主義唔係反中國人<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">（呢樣好重要）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n1. 要唱住<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">國歌</span></span>遊行<br />\n<br />\n2. or 全部人攞曬<span style=\"color: red;\">中國國旗加區旗</span>去<span style=\"color: green;\">叫5大訴求</span><br />\n<br />\n到時可以招攬回部分中國反共人士<br />\n<br />\n呢招或可逆轉形勢！大家一齊分析下。<br />\n<br />\n最後一招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbc8dbc95dea8b2004fd6c9b02d7bbda643a311a","tid":1472333,"uid":294550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:20:05.000Z","msg":"我諗都冇人會聽，因為大家好似真係未感受到大陸依家反香港反得有幾勁，大陸媒體既力量已經沫黑到冇得再黑。"},{"pid":"4bb377c1a4d91730350beb80386413d23c40d013","tid":1472333,"uid":167330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:27:00.000Z","msg":"叫連登仔唱國歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n你快啲走，我唔幫你擋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02a7bb9ff432093529f5c319d3771baaa5fdf573","tid":1472333,"uid":305905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbc8dbc95dea8b2004fd6c9b02d7bbda643a311a","tid":1472333,"uid":294550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"201